## What's next?

Once you set up the app, [[sdk-installation|install appropriate {{config.extra.arcana.sdk_name}} package]] as per the app type, and [[index-integrate|integrate the app]]. The integration method varies with the app type. As part of the integration, initialize the SDK and call appropriate functions for onboarding and allowing authenticated users to sign blockchain transactions.

!!! an-info "Save {{config.extra.arcana.app_address}}"

    A unique **{{config.extra.arcana.app_address}}** is assigned to every registered app. It is displayed on the top right of the dashboard screen. Copy and use it to integrate the app with the {{config.extra.arcana.sdk_name}}.

